name: Wiwi Gets Good
description:
A game made by elevenscuteturtle, Gorbo, and DootleSoup

Wiwi the Kiwi is an EPIC GAMER and is wants to be the best gamer around, so they travel to an abandoned mansion in search of cheat codes that will make them better than everyone else at gaming.

Esc - Pause

A, D - Move Left, Move Right

Space - Jump + Double Jump

W - Extend Legs

S - Noclip

First Cheat Code: Unlocks Double Jump and Longer Legs

Second Cheat Code: Unlocks Noclip

Final Cheat Code: It's a secret...
